<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.3.10">
<l>kaḷippuṅ kavarvumaṟṟu piṟappuppiṇi mūppiṟappaṟ</l>
<l>ṟoḷikoṇṭa cōtiyumā yuṭaṉkūṭuva teṉṟukolō</l>
<l>tuḷikkiṉṟa vāṉilañ cuṭarāḻi caṅkēnti</l>
<l>yaḷikkiṉṟa māyappirā ṉaṭiyārkaḷ kuḻāṅkaḷaiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Cutting off intoxication and attraction, going beyond the fetter of birth, cutting off old age,</l>
<l>being [with?] all the bright effulgence, when will there be uniting</l>
<l>with the throngs of servants of the illusive lord who takes care,</l>
<l>holding up the glowing disk [and] the conch, of dripping sky and earth?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
